ed.<br>Increase bombs to defeat more zombies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710390/extras/0a00aa435dc733c2eeda47b7e8d3cfed.poster.avif?t=1703003229\" width=364 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710390/extras/0a00aa435dc733c2eeda47b7e8d3cfed.webm?t=1703003229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710390/extras/0a00aa435dc733c2eeda47b7e8d3cfed.mp4?t=1703003229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Repair</h2>When a supply base is attacked by zombies, it loses its durability.<br>Without durability, you can no longer survive.<br>Use your points to repair things to survive longer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710390/extras/f9d6976d5917063b6985c3837db07735.poster.avif?t=1703003229\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710390/extras/f9d6976d5917063b6985c3837db07735.webm?t=1703003229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710390/extras/f9d6976d5917063b6985c3837db07735.mp4?t=1703003229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Defeat endless waves of zombies and survive longer.",
